    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――千歌達がサニーピースのライブに",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "特別出演すると決まった数日後",
      "startTime": 1.5800000122,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1819.9999481000002,
          "startTime": 3.3999999603
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは～",
      "startTime": 4.8333337387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk001.m4a",
      "text": "いらっしゃいませ～！　旅館『十千万』へようこそ！\n待ってたよ、さくらちゃん！",
      "startTime": 10.8092750312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "千歌ちゃん\n今日から一泊二日、お世話になります",
      "startTime": 14.4333331983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk002.m4a",
      "text": "ばっちりお世話しちゃうよ！　はぁ～、さくらちゃんが\nまた泊まりに来てくれるなんて夢みたいだよ～！",
      "startTime": 22.7730368378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "急に来てごめんね。千歌ちゃん達がサニピのライブに\n特別出演することになったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 31.2666651329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そのことで、直接会って相談したいことがあったんだ",
      "startTime": 34.3260991815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk003.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんが私に相談？",
      "startTime": 39.1537185434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。みんなのスケジュールが合わなくて\n代表して私一人で来ることになっちゃって",
      "startTime": 45.9666661502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、最近のサニピは絶好調だよね～。昨日もテレビで\n歌ってるのを観たけど、すっごくキラキラしてたよ！",
      "startTime": 54.4653742556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "調子がいいのは千歌ちゃん達のおかげだよ\nおかげでスランプから抜け出せたんだから",
      "startTime": 62.6999994835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk005.m4a",
      "text": "私は大したことしてないよ～\nって、立ち話もなんだから、場所を変えよっか",
      "startTime": 69.3426997269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tochiman-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tochiman-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "それなら行きたい所があるんだけど、いいかな？",
      "startTime": 73.2760330603,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6565.255483000002,
          "startTime": 79.8412885433
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6131.922149700003,
          "startTime": 79.40795521
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ、綺麗な海……\nやっぱりここから見る景色は格別だね",
      "startTime": 87.8333323082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk006.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんが内浦の海を好きになってくれて\n嬉しいよ～",
      "startTime": 95.172334616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、この場所で良かったの？\n部屋とかの方が落ち着いて話せるんじゃ……",
      "startTime": 99.7056679493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "……前にここへ来た時に\n千歌ちゃんが話してくれたでしょ？",
      "startTime": 105.3666656416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "ここで海を見ながら、Aqoursのみんなと\n沢山話して、いろんなことを乗り越えてきたって……",
      "startTime": 111.0666656416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いて思ったんだ。ここでなら\n話しにくいことも素直な気持ちで話せそうだなって",
      "startTime": 120.0999989749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk008.m4a",
      "text": "話しにくいこと？",
      "startTime": 125.4610668904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "……実は、今度一緒にやるライブの件で\n悩んでることがあるの",
      "startTime": 133.000003044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "Aqoursの『君のこころは輝いてるかい？』を\n千歌ちゃん達と一緒に歌いたいんだけど……",
      "startTime": 139.600003044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chk",
      "speakerName": "高海千歌",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-chk009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！　サニピのライブで\nAqoursの曲を歌うの！？",
      "startTime": 144.839300387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "うん、Aqoursの楽曲ってどれも素敵だから\n私もPVを観てすっかりファンになっちゃったんだ",
      "startTime": 152.0666920903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "特に『君のこころは輝いてるかい？』は、歌詞に\n『太陽』とか『サンシャイン』って入ってるでしょ？",
      "startTime": 161.2000254236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "太陽が明るく照らす雰囲気がサニピとも重なって\n一緒に歌うのにぴったりだと思ったの",
      "startTime": 169.8000254236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_uchiurabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "uchiurabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chk_01_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、試しに私が歌ってみたら\nしっくりこなかったんだよね",
      "startTime": 177.0666920903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
